      <title>新加坡与美国创纪录的收益率差距将因债务供应而扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/singapore-s-record-yield-gap-with-us-set-to-widen-on-debt-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着两国债务供应继续分化，新加坡超长期债券与美国国债之间的收益率差距预计将从已经创纪录的水平进一步扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-23/singapore-s-record-yield-gap-with-us-set-to-widen-on-debt-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 00:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
