      <title>联合国官员在达沃斯论坛上批评世界银行资助的私立医院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/un-official-slams-world-bank-funded-private-hospitals-at-davos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国艾滋病规划署执行主任谴责营利性医疗保健公司在低收入国家所扮演的角色，称在某些情况下，它们导致拒绝提供紧急护理和拘留病人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/un-official-slams-world-bank-funded-private-hospitals-at-davos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:54:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受库存增加和特朗普行动影响，油价连续第六天下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份行业报告显示，美国原油库存自 11 月中旬以来首次增加，市场关注特朗普总统就全球贸易做出的进一步承诺，油价小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 23:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>福蒂斯丘铁矿石出口小幅上涨，预期保持不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/fortescue-s-iron-ore-exports-edge-up-1-in-its-second-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个季度，Fortescue Ltd. 的铁矿石出货量较上年同期增长了 1%，这加剧了人们对全球最大钢铁原料生产商因中国需求减弱而导致供应过剩的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/fortescue-s-iron-ore-exports-edge-up-1-in-its-second-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 22:36:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
